{start_of_verse: Verse 1}
[G]Sunlight is [D7]gone  a wind stirs the [G]willow
Whippoorwills [D7]call  from high on the [G]hill
Deep shadows [C]fall as I wait for you by the [G]window
Soon you'll be [C]here drawing me [A7]near to you [D7]again
{end_of_verse}

{start_of_verse: Verse 2}
